description: With the badge of this award, you gain access to the 5th NFT Airdrop game of the "Magic Voodoo Dolls" OG collection. 300 people can own one of these badges, there will only be 3 NFTs that are airdropped to these 300 people. To get an airdrop you need to retweet the corresponding tweet and hold one of these badges.
name: 5th airdrop of the "Magic Voodoo Dolls" OG collection
